	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Obviously, the PowerPak is going to draw more current than an ordinary Game Pak, with the FPGA and CF slot and all, but I wouldn't think it's enough to overload the AC adapter. My guess is that the adapter is just defective (or <em>really</em> cheap), especially if it's getting too hot to touch. O_o

		

		</td>
	</tr>
