		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I got a Nintendo brand NES AC adapter today, and when using it, there is no hum in the audio.  The PowerPak works perfectly, and I love the fact that I don't need to move the PowerPak cartridge in order to remove/insert the CF card.

		

